casebody.data:
Nathaniel BRYANT and Joseph L. Gillespie
v.
Charles Wilbur BRYANT and Carl Bryant No. 74P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 14, 2017. Nathaniel Bryant, for Bryant, Nathaniel. Joseph L. Gillespie, for Gillespie, Joseph L. Paul S. Messick, Jr., Attorney at Law, for Bryant, Charles Wilbur, et al

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff (Nathaniel Bryant) on the 13th of March 2017 for Writ of Supersedeas of the judgment of the Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of March 2017."
